message.entry: Unrecognized input parameters supplied to datastore "readall".\nRecognized input parameters include ''UseParallel''.
Datastore readall with UseParallel is not supported on a thread-based parallel pool.\nChoose another parallel environment, for example 'local'.
Readall is not supported on HDFS for ''{0}''.
MDFDatastore readall with UseParallel is not supported on a thread-based parallel pool.\nUse a PARPOOL('Processes') process-based pool or a different process-based pool instead.
